Installing flask-galatea_brand
==============================

Prerequisites
-------------

 * Python 2.7 or later (http://www.python.org/)
 * trytond (http://www.tryton.org/)
 * trytond-galatea
 * trytond-galatea_brand
 * trytond-product_brand

Installation
------------

Once you've downloaded and unpacked the flask-galatea-brand source release,
copy galatea-brand directory in main flask app and rename to brand.

Edit your App flask and register a new blueprint:

from brand import brand
app.register_blueprint(brand, url_prefix='/<lang>')
